  note as InitNote
    **Initialization (SIE instance bootstrap)**

    This diagram specifies the default, auto-defined *governance* definitions
    used for Homeostasis (first-order regulation).

    At initialization time, SIE seeds these `BehavioralRule` and
    `BehavioralRuleControl` instances in the Definition Plane, and binds the
    Operator controller to exactly one BehavioralRule (CSDM invariant).

    **Mapping to feature backlog**
    - EN-1: Retention + Minimization policies (runway)
    - E-1: Evidence Preservation (governable audit/evidence substrate)
  end note

