    note right of BRC_HOM_003
      **Merged from SIE meta-governance BR-META-009 (flattened as a Control)**

      **Original applicabilityConditions:**
      - schedule.tick OR config.retentionPolicyChanged

      **Original controlSequence (intent):**
      - Compute rawWindow, derivedWindow
      - Ensure snapshots retained for governance.auditWindow
      - Apply bounding/sampling/pointer strategy for RAW
      - Expire/compact RAW + DERIVED beyond windows
      - Archive required SNAPSHOTS (replayable bundles)
      - Emit RetentionAppliedEvent

      **Coherence fix:** modeled as a Control within the single Homeostasis BehavioralRule
      to preserve the CSDM invariant “one controller mechanism implements exactly one BehavioralRule”.

      applicabilityConditions:
      {
        "type": "ComparisonExpression",
        "operator": "EQUALS",
        "left": {
          "type": "ContextVariableReferenceExpression",
          "name": "ControlIntentReceptor",
